<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Portfolio — Artist</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Syne:wght@400;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --black: #050505;
    --white: #f0ece6;
    --purple: #7b2fff;
    --purple-dim: rgba(123, 47, 255, 0.18);
    --aqua: #00e5c8;
    --aqua-dim: rgba(0, 229, 200, 0.15);
    --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    cursor: none;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* Custom cursor */
  .cursor {
    position: fixed;
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    background: var(--aqua);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    transition: transform 0.1s, width 0.3s, height 0.3s, background 0.3s;
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
  }
  .cursor-ring {
    position: fixed;
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,200,0.4);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9998;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    transition: transform 0.18s ease, width 0.4s, height 0.4s, border-color 0.3s;
  }
  body:hover .cursor { opacity: 1; }

  /* Aura canvas */
  #aura {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .aura-blob {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(100px);
    opacity: 0.25;
    animation: drift 18s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  .aura-blob:nth-child(1) {
    width: 600px; height: 600px;
    background: var(--purple);
    top: -200px; left: -150px;
    animation-duration: 20s;
  }
  .aura-blob:nth-child(2) {
    width: 500px; height: 500px;
    background: var(--aqua);
    bottom: -200px; right: -100px;
    animation-duration: 16s;
    animation-delay: -8s;
  }
  .aura-blob:nth-child(3) {
    width: 350px; height: 350px;
    background: var(--purple);
    top: 50%; left: 60%;
    opacity: 0.12;
    animation-duration: 24s;
    animation-delay: -4s;
  }
  @keyframes drift {
    0%   { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
    50%  { transform: translate(40px, 30px) scale(1.05); }
    100% { transform: translate(-30px, 50px) scale(0.97); }
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 28px 52px;
    background: rgba(5,5,5,0.5);
    backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--white);
    text-decoration: none;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  .nav-logo span { color: var(--aqua); }
  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 44px;
    list-style: none;
  }
  .nav-links a {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(240,236,230,0.55);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s;
    position: relative;
  }
  .nav-links a::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -4px; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--aqua);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.35s ease;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--white); }
  .nav-links a:hover::after,
  .nav-links a.active::after { transform: scaleX(1); }
  .nav-links a.active { color: var(--white); }

  /* PAGES */
  .page { display: none; min-height: 100vh; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .page.active { display: block; }

  /* ======================== HOME ======================== */
  #home {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 100vh;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 120px 40px 80px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--aqua);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.3s forwards;
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(80px, 14vw, 200px);
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    color: rgba(240,236,230,0.08);
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s 0.5s forwards;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .hero-name .name-outline {
    display: block;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(240,236,230,0.55);
    color: transparent;
    position: relative;
  }
  .hero-name .name-fill {
    display: block;
    color: rgba(240,236,230,0.92);
    position: relative;
  }
  .hero-name .name-fill::after {
    content: attr(data-text);
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple) 0%, var(--aqua) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    opacity: 0.35;
    filter: blur(2px);
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(13px, 1.5vw, 16px);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: rgba(240,236,230,0.4);
    margin-top: 36px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.9s forwards;
  }

  .hero-divider {
    width: 80px;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--purple), var(--aqua));
    margin: 40px auto;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 1.1s forwards;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    background: var(--glass);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: 16px 36px;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: none;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 1.3s forwards;
  }
  .hero-cta:hover {
    border-color: var(--aqua);
    background: rgba(0,229,200,0.06);
  }
  .hero-cta svg { transition: transform 0.3s; }
  .hero-cta:hover svg { transform: translateX(5px); }

  /* About strip */
  .about-strip {
    margin-top: 100px;
    padding: 80px 52px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.9s 1.5s forwards;
  }
  .about-label {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--purple);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .about-heading {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 5vw, 72px);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .about-text {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: rgba(240,236,230,0.5);
    max-width: 460px;
  }
  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    align-content: start;
    padding-top: 20px;
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple) 0%, var(--aqua) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(240,236,230,0.35);
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* ======================== GALLERY PAGES ======================== */
  .gallery-page {
    padding: 140px 52px 80px;
  }
  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 70px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    padding-bottom: 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .page-label {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--aqua);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .page-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(60px, 9vw, 130px);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(240,236,230,0.2);
    color: transparent;
    position: relative;
  }
  .page-title span {
    color: var(--white);
    -webkit-text-stroke: 0;
  }
  .page-count {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: rgba(240,236,230,0.3);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
  }

  /* Masonry grid */
  .grid {
    columns: 3;
    column-gap: 16px;
  }
  @media(max-width: 900px) { .grid { columns: 2; } }
  @media(max-width: 560px) { .grid { columns: 1; } }

  .grid-item {
    break-inside: avoid;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: none;
    background: var(--glass);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  }
  .grid-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple-dim), var(--aqua-dim));
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.4s;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .grid-item:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

  .grid-item img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
    transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
    filter: saturate(0.7) brightness(0.85);
  }
  .grid-item:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.04);
    filter: saturate(0.9) brightness(0.95);
  }

  .grid-item-info {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    padding: 20px 20px 18px;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(5,5,5,0.9) 0%, transparent 100%);
    transform: translateY(100%);
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .grid-item:hover .grid-item-info { transform: translateY(0); }

  .grid-item-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .grid-item-meta {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--aqua);
    margin-top: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* Placeholder slots */
  .slot {
    aspect-ratio: var(--ratio, 1);
    background: var(--glass);
    border: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    color: rgba(240,236,230,0.15);
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: none;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
    position: relative;
  }
  .slot:hover {
    border-color: rgba(0,229,200,0.2);
    background: rgba(0,229,200,0.03);
    color: rgba(0,229,200,0.4);
  }
  .slot svg { opacity: 0.3; transition: opacity 0.3s; }
  .slot:hover svg { opacity: 0.6; }
  .slot input[type=file] {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  /* Award badge */
  .award-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 14px; right: 14px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple) 0%, var(--aqua) 100%);
    color: var(--black);
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    z-index: 3;
  }

  /* Lightbox */
  .lightbox {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 500;
    background: rgba(5,5,5,0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    display: none;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 40px;
  }
  .lightbox.open {
    display: flex;
    animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease;
  }
  .lightbox-close {
    position: absolute;
    top: 32px; right: 40px;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(240,236,230,0.4);
    cursor: none;
    transition: color 0.3s;
    background: none;
    border: none;
  }
  .lightbox-close:hover { color: var(--aqua); }
  .lightbox img {
    max-width: 80vw;
    max-height: 80vh;
    object-fit: contain;
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  }
  .lightbox-caption {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 40px;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(240,236,230,0.35);
  }
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }

  /* Competition cards */
  .comp-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .comp-card {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: none;
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    background: var(--glass);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  }
  .comp-card img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    transition: transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94), filter 0.5s;
    filter: saturate(0.6) brightness(0.8);
  }
  .comp-card:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
    filter: saturate(0.9) brightness(0.95);
  }
  .comp-card-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(5,5,5,0.95) 0%, rgba(5,5,5,0.2) 60%, transparent 100%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 32px;
    transition: background 0.4s;
  }
  .comp-card:hover .comp-card-overlay {
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(5,5,5,0.98) 0%, rgba(5,5,5,0.5) 60%, rgba(123,47,255,0.1) 100%);
  }
  .comp-award {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 5px 12px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple), var(--aqua));
    color: var(--black);
    font-weight: 700;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    width: fit-content;
  }
  .comp-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .comp-desc {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: rgba(240,236,230,0.4);
    margin-top: 8px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.5s ease;
  }
  .comp-card:hover .comp-desc { max-height: 100px; }

  /* Upload slot comp */
  .comp-slot {
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    background: var(--glass);
    border: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    color: rgba(240,236,230,0.12);
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.63rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: none;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
    position: relative;
  }
  .comp-slot:hover {
    border-color: rgba(123,47,255,0.25);
    background: rgba(123,47,255,0.03);
    color: rgba(123,47,255,0.5);
  }
  .comp-slot input[type=file] { position:absolute; inset:0; opacity:0; cursor:pointer; }

  /* Footer */
  footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    padding: 40px 52px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .footer-logo {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: rgba(240,236,230,0.3);
  }
  .footer-note {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: rgba(240,236,230,0.18);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Cursor -->
<div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursorRing"></div>

<!-- Ambient aura -->
<div id="aura">
  <div class="aura-blob"></div>
  <div class="aura-blob"></div>
  <div class="aura-blob"></div>
</div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo" onclick="showPage('home')">A<span>.</span></a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#" onclick="showPage('home')" id="nav-home" class="active">Home</a></li>
    <li><a href="#" onclick="showPage('gallery')" id="nav-gallery">Gallery</a></li>
    <li><a href="#" onclick="showPage('personal')" id="nav-personal">Personal</a></li>
    <li><a href="#" onclick="showPage('competition')" id="nav-competition">Competition</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- ========== HOME ========== -->
<div id="home" class="page active">
  <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:100vh;padding:120px 40px 0;text-align:center;">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Visual Artist &nbsp;·&nbsp; Mixed Media &nbsp;·&nbsp; Fine Art</div>
    <div class="hero-name">
      <span class="name-outline">YOUR</span>
      <span class="name-fill" data-text="NAME">NAME</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-subtitle">Creating worlds from light, shadow, and intention.</div>
    <div class="hero-divider"></div>
    <a href="#" class="hero-cta" onclick="showPage('gallery')">
      View Portfolio
      <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path d="M3 8H13M13 8L8.5 3.5M13 8L8.5 12.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="about-strip">
    <div>
      <div class="about-label">About</div>
      <div class="about-heading">Art is<br>Vision<br>Made<br>Tangible.</div>
      <p class="about-text">
        A multidisciplinary artist working across painting, digital media, and installation. 
        My practice explores the tension between the organic and the constructed—seeking 
        moments where control dissolves into intuition. Each work is an investigation into 
        perception, materiality, and the quiet grammar of form.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-stats">
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">12+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Years of practice</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">30+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Exhibitions</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">08</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Awards won</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">∞</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Works in progress</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <div class="footer-logo">Artist Portfolio</div>
    <div class="footer-note">© 2026 — All rights reserved</div>
  </footer>
</div>

<!-- ========== GALLERY ========== -->
<div id="gallery" class="page">
  <div class="gallery-page">
    <div class="page-header">
      <div>
        <div class="page-label">Works</div>
        <div class="page-title">Gal<span>lery</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="page-count">All works — 2018–2026</div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid" id="gallery-grid">
      <!-- Slots -->
